urico, Vestito, D'Cot, and Donear NXG brands. It also provides dyed polyester and cotton yarns; and trades in garments. The company exports its products to approximately 20 countries. It serves automotive, aviation, industrial, defence, government bodies, and educational institutions through various channels, which include wholesale, retail, franchisees, agents, and dealers. Donear Industries Limited was founded in 1979 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}